# Code Citation Format

When citing or referencing code from the codebase, **always use the jumpable snippet format** so the user can click to navigate:

- First line of the code block: `startLine:endLine:relative/path/to/file.ext`
- Followed by the actual code lines

## Rules

- Include enough lines for context (typically 3–8 lines).
- **Relative path base:** Use paths relative to the **workspace file’s directory** (the folder that contains the `.code-workspace` file), not relative to `_workspace`. That directory is the parent of all repo roots (e.g. `C:\Source` when using `Source.code-workspace`).
- Use forward slashes in cited paths (e.g. `PaaS/PaaS/EPiServer.PaaS.../File.cs` for files under the PaaS solution folder).
- Line numbers must be accurate for the current file contents.
- Use this format for any code block that references a specific location in the repo.

## Workspace layout (for path resolution)

Workspace file: `C:\Source\Source.code-workspace`. Base for all relative paths: **`C:\Source`** (the directory that contains the workspace file). All repo roots are siblings under that base. Use these prefixes when citing files:

| Repo / root        | Citation path prefix (from `C:\Source`) | Example file path |
|--------------------|-----------------------------------------|-------------------|
| _workspace         | `_workspace/`                           | `_workspace/.cursor/rules/context-revision-and-code-refs.mdc` |
| dxc-deployment-automation | `dxc-deployment-automation/`   | `dxc-deployment-automation/BuildScripts/Invoke-AutomationAccountDeployment.ps1` |
| EpiCloud           | `EpiCloud/`                             | `EpiCloud/...` (path under repo root) |
| chuongnhpwshtest   | `chuongnhpwshtest/`                     | `chuongnhpwshtest/util/runner.ps1` |
| PaaS               | `PaaS/PaaS/` for solution files         | `PaaS/PaaS/EPiServer.PaaS.ProvisioningWorker.Base/MessageHandlers/HandleCompleteCustomHostnameProvisioning.cs` |

If the editor is opened as a single folder (e.g. only `C:\Source\_workspace`), paths to files in other repos are outside that root and click-to-open may not work. Open via the workspace file for correct resolution.

## Example

Format: ```startLine:endLine:relative/path followed by the code block. Relative path is from `C:\Source`. Examples: `55:58:dxc-deployment-automation/BuildScripts/Invoke-AutomationAccountDeployment.ps1`; `1:10:PaaS/PaaS/EPiServer.PaaS.ProvisioningWorker.Base/MessageHandlers/HandleCompleteCustomHostnameProvisioning.cs`; `1:5:_workspace/.cursor/rules/context-revision-and-code-refs.mdc`; `1:10:chuongnhpwshtest/util/runner.ps1`.
